{"tid":1542513,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［腦震盪］ABC策略，反制中聯辦重兵。","createTime":"2019-09-05T01:19:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T02:31:17.000Z","uid":52200,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d385aeac7fc3521f8fe4c608e79d7e4ddb5e3aad","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:19:08.000Z","msg":"ABC策略 = Anything But Chinese<br />\n<br />\n中文翻譯是：除了中國，任何都可以。<br />\n<br />\n既然成個8月，中聯辦門前都唔俾人示威，我哋就唔去中聯辦，今個月同下個月開始，每個星期六、日集中去一個領事館舉國旗、唱國歌，要求制裁港共政權！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🇬🇧🇫🇷🇧🇪🇰🇷🇯🇵🇹🇼🇺🇸🇦🇺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sir, this way!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"83fd77b78ad1e5cf30a186d17ee674ead1f912c1","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:19:50.000Z","msg":"1/100"},{"pid":"6a37fbb694f39ebda434c59069107d0ecbe202e7","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"2/100"},{"pid":"ead75742ed4efcdaf0161994630f3dd0b1802abf","tid":1542513,"uid":177213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:21:07.000Z","msg":"大佬 受害者快d聯絡律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔係我地永遠都唔知當日既真相<br />\n<br />\n(手動轉戴)<br />\n<br />\n最快兩日，黨鐵就可以刪除831晚太子站cctv，到時你、被防暴圍毆嘅抗爭者同乘客，唔會再攞得返公道。<br />\n<br />\n之前講過無論你係受傷定受驚，都可以向香港警察或港鐵提出民事訴訟，申請要法庭強制命令黨鐵交出831當晚既CCTV。 有法庭命令，黨鐵唔交就係藐視法庭！😡<br />\n<br />\n成班義務律師大狀已經準備就緒，但到而家仲未有任何831受害人contact 義務律師！🤯😔<br />\n其實受害人唔使怕有咩隱憂，例如自爆、金錢、時間，義務律師會同你傾咗先，商量吓再決定告唔告，一切內容絕對保密。🤐👌<br />\n<br />\n港鐵每7-28日就會清一次cctv，換言之我哋最快得返兩日去揾證據，時間一過，在場所有人受到嘅傷害、屈辱，將會永遠石沉大海，而毆打你哋嘅武裝分子繼續逍遙法外，無後果地打壓香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n就喺呢兩日，你可以選擇還831傷者一個公道，將黑警暴行昭告天下。就算你唔喺現場，都請你幫手推post，比在場者見到為止。<br />\n<br />\n831受害者請盡快聯絡以下團體：<br />\n<br />\n1. 星火: 9819 0979 <br />\n2. 民陣:6549 9452 <br />\n3. 民權: 9463 2945 <br />\n4. 伍展邦:2608 1400"},{"pid":"56f982f30bcd818f2b933dda7b37642b1825c331","tid":1542513,"uid":18827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都得"},{"pid":"bfa1ffc3f74715bcd07e69f4b68c0e807464ae6a","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:22:37.000Z","msg":"3/100"},{"pid":"a6b5341015cc763c1e3758cd45175b1385087535","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:24:26.000Z","msg":"4/100"},{"pid":"b93ca5b904236a4984ab5d40ec0b1e1e1992e84d","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:24:39.000Z","msg":"5/100"},{"pid":"1230691ed36fc28e1076a95df00d8adb7f6e3d97","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:24:53.000Z","msg":"6/100"},{"pid":"c3172cdd9a5a4dbe46b1c72542f77af4ef4da556","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"7/100"},{"pid":"7f6a825b5dcec1b86477889bfeda2b30b4755b1a","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:25:14.000Z","msg":"8/100"},{"pid":"89b8acc7107081a382696425349632424aaa0d6c","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:25:34.000Z","msg":"9/100"},{"pid":"bcf0a5f8f87383e7851e7436db071bd847c9ef6f","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"10/100"},{"pid":"7b331421c52dca69fd8aceb70095b1d24dbb1e72","tid":1542513,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T01:26:10.000Z","msg":"1